title: Reborn Ranker – Gravity User
description: Description: “Who needs a bandit, anyway?” That’s the last thing Ikoma Ichinose, a bandit-class hunter, heard before he got kicked out of his party and ran into a monster that would kill him. But he was given a second chance at life in the form of a time-turning pocket watch. “Yeah, who needs a bandit?” This time, Ikoma chooses to be a gravity master to have a shot at becoming the greatest hunter of all time. This time I will become… the greatest adventurer! Adventurers aim for the strongest in hidden classes, 冒険者は隠しクラス〈重力使い〉で最強を目指す, 히든클래스 중력자로 최강을 노린다, ２周目冒険者は隠しクラス ＜重力使い＞で最強を目指す Reborn Ranker – Gravity User, Hidden Class Gravity User, Aiming for the Strongest as a Hidden Class Graviton
alternative_titles: Adventurers aim for the strongest in hidden classes
